.jpg" /> <img class="owl-lazy img-fluid" data-src="https://setc.id/res/images/umkm/IMG_20201118_110540_HDR.jpg" /> <img class="owl-lazy img-fluid" data-src="https://setc.id/res/images/umkm/IMG_20201118_111019_HDR.jpg" /> </div> </div> <div class="umkm-modal-content"> <div class="umkm-modal-thumbnail"> <img class="img-fluid" src="https://setc.id/res/images/umkm/Iwan Permana-Lumpia cik Renren.jpg" /> </div> <div class="umkm-modal-caption"> <div class="umkm-modal-name">	Lumpia Cik Renren (Iwan Permana) </div> <div class="umkm-modal-description"> <p>	Dengan bekal ilmu, pengalaman, dan semangat untuk mengangkat kuliner khas kota Semarang, Bapak Iwan mendirikan Lumpia Cik Renren hingga dapat menyerap lulusan SMK Tataboga sekitar.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div id="umkm-modal-19" class="umkm-modal modal fade" data-keyboard="false" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="umkmModalLabel" aria-hidden="true"> <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered" role="document"> <div class="modal-content"> <div class="modal-body"> <div class="modal-close" data-dismiss="modal">X</div> <div class="umkm-modal-image"> <div class="umkm-modal-image-carousel owl-carousel"> <img class="owl-lazy img-fluid" data-src="https://setc.id/res/images/umkm/1.jpg" /> <img class="owl-lazy img-fluid" data-src="https://setc.id/res/images/umkm/2.jpg" /> <img class="owl-lazy img-fluid" data-src="https://setc.id/res/images/umkm/3.jpg" /> <img class="owl-lazy img-fluid" data-src="https://setc.id/res/images/umkm/4.jpg" /> <img class="owl-lazy img-fluid" data-src="https://setc.id/res/images/umkm/5.jpg" /> </div> </div> <div class="umkm-modal-content"> <div class="umkm-modal-thumbnail"> <img class="img-fluid" src="https://setc.id/res/images/umkm/P_20201202_121901 - Pamella Tri A Mellin Gallery.jpg" /> </div> <div class="umkm-modal-caption"> <div class="umkm-modal-name">	MeLLin Gallery (Pamella Tri Arrylia) </div> <div class="umkm-modal-variant">	Varian Produk: Kitoys elephant, Ki